  <scopecontent id="aspace_f2b5a038caba8486f6ef0d283441d735">
    <head>Scope and Content Notes</head>
<p>This collection contains stockholder and board of director's meeting minutes, mortgages, deeds, bonds, and lease records for the North Side Laundry Company of Allegheny City, Pa. (now Pittsburgh's North Side) for the years 1877-1943. The records are arranged chronologically by subject.</p>  </scopecontent>
